[04:31.79]	O heavy times, begetting such events!
[04:35.71]	From London by the king was I press'd forth;
[04:40.37]	My father, being the Earl of Warwick's man,
[04:44.85]	Came on the part of York, press'd by his master;
[04:49.79]	And I, who at his hands received my life, him
